INTEREST EXPENSE

: INTEREST EXPENSE INCREASED IN 2016 DUE TO HIGHER AVERAGE DEBT BALANCES AND HIGHER U.S. BORROWING COSTS. INTEREST EXPENSE INCREASED SLIGHTLY IN 2015 COMPARED TO 2014, DESPITE SIGNIFICANTLY HIGHER DEBT LEVELS, HELPED BY LOWER AVERAGE INTEREST RATES.

